  <h1>Healthcare Workers CRS Calculator 2026<br><span style="font-weight:400;font-size:0.82em;">Free Express Entry Points Tool for Nurses, Doctors & Healthcare Professionals</span></h1>
  <p>Calculate your CRS score for Canada's Healthcare category-based Express Entry draws. Covers all healthcare NOC codes — doctors, nurses, pharmacists, dentists, and more.</p>
